{"tid":2101568,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡錫進：民主自由是社會主義核心價值觀  五分鐘就刪除！","createTime":"2020-07-10T02:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:34:41.000Z","uid":205884,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"23c3af31116e201df83a242052a495302719d379","tid":2101568,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDtOc6X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDtOc6X.jpg&h=c00290c3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRSOXyD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRSOXyD.jpg&h=1e497e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有Backup，佳句摘錄：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老胡一直认为，中国需要不断<span class=\"red\">推动宪法第一条与宪法第三十五条在现实中的相互协调</span>，这是中国的必由之路。<br />\n<br />\n    <span class=\"orange\">     <blockquote>第一條：社會主義制度是中華人民共和國的根本制度。中國共產黨領導是中國特色社會主義最本質的特徵。<br />\n        第三十五條：中華人民共和國公民有言論、出版、集會、結社、遊行、示威的自由。</blockquote></span><br />\n<br />\n官方要在不断塑造、加强社会凝聚力的同时，<span class=\"red\">积极探索扩大社会的表达空间，增强体制的包容性</span>。<br />\n<br />\n每遇官员，我就利用机会提意见，<span class=\"red\">破除官僚主义是关键项</span>，官员的工作既要对上负责，也一定要对下负责，要真正争取民心。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>關鍵就關鍵，乜差野關鍵項？中國人唔識寫中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">民主、自由可都是社会主义核心价值观里的明确内容</span>，千万别忽视了。<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></p>"},{"pid":"a3b018c39c6a68a82c8de24887d0e489b090317f","tid":2101568,"uid":205884,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"操他妈的胡锡进，吃里扒外的美帝主义走狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji